             was indicted for <rs id="t17980110-28-off149" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17980110-28-off149" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17980110-28-off149" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     <persName id="t17980110-28-victim318" type="victimName">
                        Thomas 
                        Acton
                     <interp inst="t17980110-28-victim318" type="surname" value="Acton"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17980110-28-victim318" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17980110-28-victim318" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  , about the hour of eleven in the night of the <rs id="t17980110-28-cd150" type="crimeDate">28th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980110-28-off149 t17980110-28-cd150"></join>, and stealing a hempen bag, value 6d. 2700 halfpence, and 24 farthings, value 5l. 12s. 6d.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t17980110-28-victim319" type="victimName">
                  Thomas 
                  Nichal
               <interp inst="t17980110-28-victim319" type="surname" value="Nichal"></interp>
